        "text": "Here's a comprehensive summary of debugging capabilities in this environment:\n\n---\n\n## \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Debugging Capabilities\n\n### State Info (from `~/.openclaw/state/internal.json`)\n- **Plugins:** `status-skill`\n- **Workflows:** `reminder-workflow`\n\n---\n\n### Core Tools\n\n| Tool | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| **`openclaw status`** | Full system overview \u2014 OS, node, gateway, agents, memory, sessions |\n| **`openclaw status --deep`** | Deep probe with channel testing |\n| **`openclaw status --all`** | Shareable full status output |\n| **`openclaw logs --follow`** | Live log tailing via RPC |\n| **`openclaw logs --json`** | Structured JSON log output |\n| **`openclaw security audit`** | Security scan (2 warnings currently: no auth rate limiting, extensions exist without `plugins.allow`) |\n| **`openclaw security audit --deep`** | Extended security report |\n\n---\n\n### Session Debugging (`session-logs` skill)\nSession logs at: `~/.openclaw/agents/<agentId>/sessions/`\n- **`sessions.json`** \u2014 Index mapping session keys to IDs\n- **`<session-id>.jsonl`** \u2014 Full transcript per session\n\nUseful queries:\n```bash\n# List all sessions by date/size\n# Extract user/assistant messages\n# Search for keywords across all sessions\n# Get cost breakdown per session\n# Tool usage breakdown\n```\n\n---\n\n### Model Usage (`model-usage` skill)\n- Uses `codexbar` CLI (macOS only per skill, but status shows Linux)\n- `python /app/skills/model-usage/scripts/model_usage.py --provider codex --mode current|all`\n\n---\n\n### Available Skills (52 total)\nKey debugging-relevant skills:\n- **healthcheck** \u2014 Host security hardening & risk tolerance\n- **skill-creator** \u2014 Create/audit skills\n- **session-logs** \u2014 Session history analysis (jq-based)\n- **model-usage** \u2014 Per-model cost tracking\n- **coding-agent** \u2014 Code debugging/development\n\n---\n\n### Session Management Tools\n| Function | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `sessions_list` | List active sessions with filters |\n| `sessions_history` | Fetch message history for a session |\n| `sessions_send` | Send message to another session |\n| `sessions_spawn` | Spawn isolated sub-agent or ACP session |\n| `subagents` | List/kill/steer sub-agents |\n| `session_status` | Usage + time + cost card (`/status`) |\n\n---\n\n### Cron/Scheduling Debug\n- `cron status` \u2014 Check cron scheduler state\n- `cron list` \u2014 List all jobs (incl. disabled)\n- `cron runs <jobId>` \u2014 Get job run history\n\n---\n\n### Current Environment\n- **Runtime:** `agent=cd002-real-smoke-1-3a44c6ff` (this session)\n- **Host:** Linux WSL2 (6.6.87.2), Node v24.14.0\n- **Gateway:** `ws://127.0.0.1:18789`, reachable locally\n- **577 active sessions**, default model: `minimax/m2.7` (256k ctx)\n- **Update available:** npm `2026.3.13`\n\n---\n\n### Security Warnings (2)\n1. **No auth rate limiting** \u2014 `gateway.auth.rateLimit` not configured\n2. **Extensions exist without `plugins.allow`** \u2014 discovered plugins may load\n\nRun `openclaw security audit --deep` for full report.",
